title: Split Ends - The Year of Positivity and Possibilities
itunes:title: Split Ends - The Year of Positivity and Possibilities
description:
On the latest episode of Split Ends, Colleen and Erica are back to ring in the New Year, but first they share their favorite John Madden moments. Then we go through a headline check with some awkward post game interviews, questionable behavior in a church on Christmas Eve, and mayo. To close out 2021, we share some New Year's Resolutions for a few teams, including the Eagles and the Seahawks.
